title: Random FPS Drops

I may not have needed your r3d log, since it's pretty lengthy and contains minimal context, but I appreciate you offering it. It looks like your display driver is over a year old, and there may be an updated one available directly from Intel. This and other steps are covered inside our [FPS Guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting), so I recommend working through all the steps included to confirm this isn't caused by common misconfigurations.

Let me know if those steps caused any change.
